  "keyFeatures": [
    "Client-side batch image processing with no server required",
    "Image optimization using browser-image-compression",
    "Format conversion between JPG, PNG, WEBP, and GIF",
    "Flexible resizing with pixel or percentage units",
    "Intelligent cropping with position control",
    "Batch file renaming with multiple patterns",
    "ZIP download for processed images",
    "Brand customization with logo and color themes",
    "Memory-efficient processing for large files",
    "Responsive UI built with Ant Design"
